job_description:
About us

Superfiliate is ushering in the next era of growth for e-commerce businesses by introducing new social buying paradigms that make it fun and rewarding for individuals to tell people about the products and brands they love. We see a world where the brands that people discover are no longer dictated by who will pay top dollar for their attention, but rather by the recommendations of those they trust.

We’re a team of builders where everyone has a voice and the best ideas win, not the loudest voice in the room. We have designed our culture to create an environment where people are empowered to do their best work and continuously improve and grow.

Our team is fully distributed with offices in Los Angeles, CA, and Florianópolis, Brazil but look for every opportunity we can to get together to build meaningful relationships and comradery beyond the work we do on a daily basis.

Full Stack Engineer

Your responsibilities

  • Design, Build, test, and deploy code using our best practices;
  • Help to identify, prioritize, and execute tasks in the software development life cycle;
  • Team up with the product and design team to define, plan, and execute deliverables;
  • Partner with the Lead Engineer and fellow Software Engineers in conducting requirements discovery, solution presentations, and various workshop formats;
  • Help to write documentation about our architecture, engineering processes, and best practices;

We are looking for a Lead Engineer who has:

  • 3+ years of working experience with our back-end stack: Ruby, Rails, Sidekiq, GraphQL, Relational Databases;
  • Hands-on experience with our front-end stack: React, Preact, Typescript, NextJS, SWR;
  • Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, dynamic startup environment;
  • Ability to maintain a positive mood and inspire coworkers, wherever they are in the world;
  • Pragmatic and product-oriented mindset;
  • As a bonus, having experience working with Shopify or any other e-commerce platform;
  • As a bonus, having previous experience with event sourcing architecture;

Perks & Benefits

  • Superfiliate offers a competitive salary (in $USD);
  • Paid time off + local holidays;
  • Work from home stipend to make sure every team member has the equipment they need to be most productive;
  • Weekly lunches - the only catch: you have to share in our Slack channel!
  • Company offsites - we hold team retreats to get together and connect in person;
  • A culture of creative, passionate people who truly enjoy the work they do and the people they do it with;
